T1  - On Option Pricing Bounds
AU  - RITCHKEN, PETER H.
Y1  - 1985/09/01
PY  - 1985
DA  - 1985/09/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-6261.1985.tb02373.x
